{"title":"Polymorph","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Polymorph","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                      |\n| - | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | Randomly alters the form of a creature. It is especially effective against shape-changing creatures. |\n\n**Polymorph** is a monster-only spell that inflicts different effects depending on whether its target is a player or a monster. Players are temporarily [transformed](/Transformation \"Transformation\") into a [bad form](/Bad_form \"Bad form\"), while monsters are transformed into another monster of the same [holiness](/Holiness \"Holiness\") with similar HD. [Mutation resistance](/Mutation_resistance \"Mutation resistance\") provides no protection from polymorph, but [willpower](/Willpower \"Willpower\") and worshiping [Zin](/Zin \"Zin\") may protect you.\n\nThe following enemies cast Polymorph:\n\n- G [![Great orb of eyes.png](/images/3/3c/Great_orb_of_eyes.png)](/File:Great_orb_of_eyes.png) **[Great orb of eyes](/Great_orb_of_eyes \"Great orb of eyes\")**\n- @ [![Psyche.png](/images/a/a9/Psyche.png)](/File:Psyche.png) **[Psyche](/Psyche \"Psyche\")**\n\nThe following enemies may be able to cast Polymorph, depending on their spell set:\n\n- & [![Pandemonium lord.png](/images/c/c6/Pandemonium_lord.png)](/File:Pandemonium_lord.png) **[Pandemonium lord](/Pandemonium_lord \"Pandemonium lord\")** (3.4% chance)\n\nPlayers (and other monsters) may use a similar effect by zapping a [wand of polymorph](/Wand_of_polymorph \"Wand of polymorph\").\n\n## History\n\n| [![Polymorph.png](/images/e/ec/Polymorph.png)](/File:Polymorph.png) Polymorph |                                                                                  |\n| :---------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Level                                                                         | 4                                                                                |\n| School1                                                                       | [Transmutation](/Transmutations \"Transmutations\")                                |\n| School2                                                                       | [Hexes](/Hexes \"Hexes\")                                                          |\n| Source(s)                                                                     | [Book of Transfigurations](/Book_of_Transfigurations \"Book of Transfigurations\") |\n| [Casting noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                   | 3                                                                                |\n| [Spell noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                     | 0                                                                                |\n\n- Prior to [0.14](/0.14 \"0.14\"), the Polymorph spell was available to players.\n- Prior to [0.12](/0.12 \"0.12\"), this spell was called [Polymorph Other](/Polymorph_Other \"Polymorph Other\"). When used on the player by a monster, it had the same effects as [Malmutate](/Malmutate \"Malmutate\").\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Polymorph - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Polymorph\",\"wgTitle\":\"Polymorph\",\"wgCu